<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <style>
           .about-us {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .about-us:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }

        .about-us-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            padding-right: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .about-text h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #2196F3;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .about-text span {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4CAF50;
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .about-image img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar Placeholder -->
    <div id="navbar-container"></div>

    <!-- About Us Section -->
    <section class="about-us">
        <div class="about-us-content">
            <!-- Left Content -->
            <div class="about-text">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
<p>    

 We believe that every act of kindness has the power to transform lives. Our mission is to bridge the gap between donors and impactful causes, providing a centralized platform where you can contribute to a variety of initiatives—from supporting NGOs to contributing to India’s government donation schemes like PM CARES.

We aim to make giving simple, secure, and transparent, so you can track your contributions and see the direct impact of your generosity. Whether you’re looking to donate to education, healthcare, disaster relief, or environmental causes, We offer a trusted and easy way to make a real difference.

Join us in building a better tomorrow, one donation at a time."
</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Image -->
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="/about.jpg" alt="About Us Image" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section> 
</body>
</html>